Privacy Policy

Effective Date:16 Aug, 2024

Introduction

Welcome to Digital Vision Board ("we," "our," "us"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled safely and responsibly. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our app.

Information We Collect

1. Personal Information: When you register for an account, we collect your username, profile picture, and email address for login purposes.
2. Photos: If you choose to upload images to your vision board, we will access your device's photos to facilitate this feature. We only use this access to allow you to upload and manage your images within the app.
3. Advertisement ID: We use your advertisement ID to deliver personalized advertisements and analyze app usage.

How We Use Your Information

1. To Provide and Improve Services: We use your personal information to create and manage your account, enable you to upload images, and enhance your app experience.
2. To Personalize Advertising: Your advertisement ID helps us deliver ads that are relevant to you and analyze advertising effectiveness.

Data Retention

We retain your information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by law. You can delete your account at any time through the app, which will remove your personal information from our system.

Your Rights

1. Access and Update: You can access and update your personal information through your account settings in the app.
2. Account Deletion: You have the right to delete your account and associated data at any time through the app.

Data Security

We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.

Third-Party Services

Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third parties.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the app, and we encourage you to review this policy periodically.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at team.cuboidinc@gmail.com
